"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-caeleb-dressel-katie-ledecky-swimming-battle-against-time\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Heading into big meets, swimmers notoriously lie to themselves.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"big meets\", \"from\": 13, \"to\": 22}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 24, \"to\": 32}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The internal dialogue says that a lifetime-best performance is coming, that their training has led them to the point where they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll inevitably see a number flash on the scoreboard next to their names that they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve never produced before.\\u00c2 It isn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t always a lie, of course.\", \"from\": 64, \"to\": 340, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The internal dialogue\", \"from\": 64, \"to\": 85}, {\"ngram\": \"a lifetime-best performance\", \"from\": 96, \"to\": 123}, {\"ngram\": \"their training\", \"from\": 140, \"to\": 154}, {\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 180}, {\"ngram\": \"they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 196}, {\"ngram\": \"a number flash\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 226}, {\"ngram\": \"their names\", \"from\": 253, \"to\": 264}, {\"ngram\": \"they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve\", \"from\": 270, \"to\": 279}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 303}, {\"ngram\": \"always a lie\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 327}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s never always true, and the lies can become more brazen as swimmers get older.\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 351}, {\"ngram\": \"the lies\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"more brazen\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 406}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Believing that a new level of greatness is always within reach is a powerful drug.\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 512, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new level\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 456}, {\"ngram\": \"greatness\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 469}, {\"ngram\": \"reach\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 492}, {\"ngram\": \"a powerful drug\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Which is why Caeleb Dressel startled a room full of reporters with an honest admission Saturday night at the U.S. Olympic Trials in Indianapolis.\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 527, \"end\": 541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caeleb Dressel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\"}, {\"begin\": 628, \"end\": 642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"score\": 0.8581582794952675, \"rank\": 0.038961038961052005, \"text\": \"Olympic Trials\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\"}, {\"begin\": 646, \"end\": 658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis_500\", \"score\": 0.9985833094000108, \"rank\": 0.0010763352833510565, \"text\": \"Indianapolis\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis_500\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis_500\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a room\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 557}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 575}, {\"ngram\": \"an honest admission\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t know if I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll ever go a best time ever again,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Dressel said.\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 665}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"a best time\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThat\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s hard to say out loud.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Compare and contrast that with the words three years ago from another all-time great who is, like Dressel, 27 years old.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m always striving to be better than I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve ever been, and it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not easy when your times are world records,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Katie Ledecky said during the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 1063, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1018, \"end\": 1031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"loud.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Compare\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"the words\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 815}, {\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 880}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 946}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"your times\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 993}, {\"ngram\": \"world records\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1011}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m really tough on myself.\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1096, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1072}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the attitude I have\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094I literally approach each race with a belief that I can swim a best time, and that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s pretty darned tough.\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1239, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the attitude\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"each race\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"a belief\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s why I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve been so successful over the years, because I approach every single race with the attitude that anything can happen, and I can break world records this race.\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1420, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1297}, {\"ngram\": \"every single race\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1335}, {\"ngram\": \"the attitude\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1353}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"world records\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1409}, {\"ngram\": \"this race\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m going to step up and throw down.\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a real blessing and a curse to have that attitude.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Both are legends in the sport who are chasing their own greatness, trying to catch up to times that were achieved at younger ages.\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1652, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a real blessing\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"a curse\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1494}, {\"ngram\": \"attitude.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"legends\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"their own greatness\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1586}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1615}, {\"ngram\": \"younger ages\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Realistic or futile, that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s always the goal.\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Realistic or futile, that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s always the goal\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a very successful meet here, winning two events and making an Olympic relay in a third, Dressel is closer to his younger self.\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very successful meet\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1729}, {\"ngram\": \"two events\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic relay\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"a third\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1793}, {\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"his younger self\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s trying to dial back to the prime years of 2019\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009321, when he was breaking world and American records.\\u00c2 His winning time in the 100 butterfly Saturday was only .32 off what he did in Omaha three years ago at Trials, and it vaults him near the top of the crowded world rankings in that event heading into Paris.\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 2151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1925, \"end\": 1933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9991461284661525, \"rank\": 0.0008514786164099919, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2024, \"end\": 2029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omaha_people\", \"score\": 0.7684660690807047, \"rank\": 0.30122520390235036, \"tex