\"to\": 3253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She started with a 3:58.35 in the 400 freestyle, which was three seconds faster than she was at Olympic Trials in 2021 and only two seconds off her American record from 2016.\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3415, \"end\": 3423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9991461284661525, \"rank\": 0.0008514786164099919, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 3:58.35\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3293}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400 freestyle\", \"from\": 3297, \"to\": 3314}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Trials\", \"from\": 3363, \"to\": 3377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Next up was the 200 free, which she won comfortably but did not break 1:55 and has not broken 1:54 since the Rio de Janeiro Olympics in \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009916.\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3551, \"end\": 3565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4898561215936425e-14, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009916\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the 1,500, Ledecky destroyed the field as usual but wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t thrilled with her time of 15:37.35, which was faster than the 2021 Trials but 17 seconds off the world record she set in this same city six years ago.\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 3599, \"to\": 3606}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3626}, {\"ngram\": \"her time\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3671}, {\"ngram\": \"15:37.35\", \"from\": 3675, \"to\": 3683}, {\"ngram\": \"