 \"to\": 4285}, {\"ngram\": \"aging\", \"from\": 4289, \"to\": 4294}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Time is undefeated, which makes the belief in turning back the clock\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094literally and figuratively\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094more difficult.\", \"from\": 4296, \"to\": 4411, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Time\", \"from\": 4296, \"to\": 4300}, {\"ngram\": \"the belief\", \"from\": 4328, \"to\": 4338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWhen you are 19, 20, 21, you keep chipping away, chipping away, chipping away,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Dressel said.\", \"from\": 4413, \"to\": 4511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 4498, \"to\": 4505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI am still working harder than ever, finding outlets, finding every path I can take to shave those couple tenths.\", \"from\": 4512, \"to\": 4628, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 4512, \"to\": 4516}, {\"ngram\": \"outlets\", \"from\": 4560, \"to\": 4567}, {\"ngram\": \"every path\", \"from\": 4577, \"to\": 4587}, {\"ngram\": \"those couple tenths\", \"from\": 4608, \"to\": 4627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know.\", \"from\": 4629, \"to\": 4643, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know if I can do that.\", \"from\": 4644, \"to\": 4675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really good at racing.\", \"from\": 4676, \"to\": 4703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You put me in a race, I will make it close, as close as I possibly can, even if I have to try to kill myself to get there.\", \"from\": 4704, \"to\": 4826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will put myself in those situations.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Caeleb Dressel has put himself in Paris in multiple events as a three-time Olympian.\", \"from\": 4827, \"to\": 4954, \"entit